extendedInfo.description: 7 DAY FREE TRIAL My Mobile Watchdog (MMWD) is the very best parental control app for your child's Android phone. Put this app on your children's Android phone now to keep them safe. Be aware that children may not like this app even though it is keeping them safe and providing you, the parent, with peace of mind.If you have downloaded the My Mobile Watchdog Parent app on your own Android phone and created your account on it then you were directed to this page and are almost done with the setup. All you need to do now is download this free My Mobile Watchdog Child app onto your child's phone and login with your user name and password. You have already paid for the monthly service through the My Mobile Watchdog Parent app. You will be billed $4.95 each month for up to five children on this service. 7 DAY FREE TRIALAt this point, you should have received a text on your child's phone with the link which took you to this page. Now, * Tap Install above to download the app.* Open the app and tap Login or Create an Account.* Select either the monthly ($4.95) or annual ($44.95) pricing plan and proceed with payment.* Finally, tap the Activate button on the Device Administrator screen and then tap OK. * You're all done! The MMWD Childâs App will begin syncing and you are now protecting your child!Go to the My Mobile Watchdog Parent app OR www.mymobilewatchdog.com to adjust the permissions for your children and track their activities.For help or support, please email support1@mymobilewatchdog.com. or call us toll free at 888-377-8200

reviews.comment: Supposedly my mom trusts me, yet she still got this on my phone. The way i see it is if you feel your child needs this you shouldn\'t allow them a phone in the first place. Anyway, as to the app, it crashes a ton for me and since i download new apps all the time I\'m having to always put in the password whenever i want to get on something, which makes me just give up on my phone for a bit at times. My phone also freezes a bunch  which i think is a result of this app, plus it takes a lot of my battery power.

reviews.title: Awesome tool

reviews.title: Great way to keep kids safe!!

reviews.title: Its great

I can see all text msges they get and send and see what they are talking about.  You can sit up to send u a txt or send to ur email.  I block games when she gets into trouble which she doesn\'t like that. But this is great a must need for parents

reviews.title: BIG Mistake.
reviews.comment: I downloaded this app thinking it would back up my text messages, & obviously i was wrong. I didn\'t know this was a program for parents to install on their child\'s phone, and now i dont know how to uninstall it! I know the password and everything, obviously since im the one who installed it. But i dont know how to get it off? Can you tell me how? I know the password & everything i just can\'t seem to figure out how to take it out, i dont need this app.

reviews.title: Awesome
reviews.comment: I\'m 14 and my mom trusted me before I did what I did. It was pretty bad.. anyways my mom got this app because she lost her trust which I get. And its a great app. She\'s gets my texts and stuff but not like there\'s anything to hide from her. And the previous apps on my phone that she didn\'t uninstall aren\'t blocked which is okay. I don\'t have Facebook instagram or snapchat anymore and I can\'t install it without her knowin. Its not an invasion of privacy. Its for your own safety.
